    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"홍승아 기술 블로그","description":"홍승아 기술 블로그에 오신걸 환영합니다.","author":"홍승아","type":"website","siteUrl":"https://seungahhong.github.io"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>Blog Theme</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Jekyll theme 테마를 이용한 개인 블로그 만들기</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://theorydb.github.io/envops/2019/05/21/envops-blog-how-to-use-git/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">Blog Theme 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://theorydb.github.io/envops/2019/05/02/envops-blog-theme/#clean-blog-%ED%85%8C%EB%A7%88%EB%A5%BC-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%ED%95%9C-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">Blog Theme 2</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Open Icon</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>웹페이지 개발시 필요한 아이콘을 무료로 다운 받을 수 있는 페이지</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 946px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/b2dbf/freeicon.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.140625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/4fae8/freeicon.webp 256w,\n/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/2bf0f/freeicon.webp 512w,\n/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/6b2e4/freeicon.webp 946w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 946px) 100vw, 946px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/e3135/freeicon.png 256w,\n/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/06341/freeicon.png 512w,\n/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/b2dbf/freeicon.png 946w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 946px) 100vw, 946px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/47e49aeca480fdb7cc4b653549dce330/b2dbf/freeicon.png\"\n            alt=\"Free Icon\"\n            title=\"Free Icon\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.freepik.com/popular-icons\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">Icon 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://simpleicons.org/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">Icon 2</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Open Color</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>글꼴, 배경, 테두리 등과 같은 UI에서 사용하는 Color 집합체를 정리한 페이지</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 749px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/2ab73/opencolor.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.03125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/4fae8/opencolor.webp 256w,\n/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/2bf0f/opencolor.webp 512w,\n/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/9c16c/opencolor.webp 749w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/e3135/opencolor.png 256w,\n/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/06341/opencolor.png 512w,\n/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/2ab73/opencolor.png 749w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/409a3631852ecd8e3cb8a54b5a04230b/2ab73/opencolor.png\"\n            alt=\"Open Color\"\n            title=\"Open Color\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://yeun.github.io/open-color/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">Open Color</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/open-color\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">npm Open Color</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Surge.sh 로 무료로 정적 웹 어플리케이션 배포</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/58709/surge.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.59375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/4fae8/surge.webp 256w,\n/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/2bf0f/surge.webp 512w,\n/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/d71bc/surge.webp 1024w,\n/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/4fd99/surge.webp 1108w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/e3135/surge.png 256w,\n/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/06341/surge.png 512w,\n/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/42a19/surge.png 1024w,\n/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/58709/surge.png 1108w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e8afb027842cbfd2a1b3052ce1e3ac65/42a19/surge.png\"\n            alt=\"surge\"\n            title=\"surge\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Surge.sh는 정적 웹 어플리케이션을 귀찮은 가입 과정 혹은 복잡한 설정 과정 없이 배포할 수 있는 프론트엔드를 위한 호스팅 서비스이다. 아주 큰 특징은 지금 코드를 작성하고 있는 IDE 혹은 터미널에서 벗어나지 않고, 커맨드라인에서 명령어 몇줄로 아주 간단하게 배포할 수 있다는 것이 특징이다. 그리고, 가격도 개인적인 프로젝트 수준에서는 무료 플랜을 사용해도 정말 무방하다. 별도의 서버가 필요없거나 API 서버가 따로 있는 경우의 정적 웹사이트, 웹 어플리케이션, SPA 등의 배포에 아주 최적화 되어있다. 이런 장점에도 의외로 국내자료가 매우 없기 때문에 직접 소개를 해보려 한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://hudi.kr/surge-sh-%EB%A1%9C-%EB%AC%B4%EB%A3%8C%EB%A1%9C-%EC%A0%95%EC%A0%81-%EC%9B%B9-%EC%96%B4%ED%94%8C%EB%A6%AC%EC%BC%80%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98-%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\">참고사이트</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Snippet</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>정형화된 코드를 prefix를 입력해서 바로 자동완성 시켜주는 기능을 snippert이라고 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>intellij</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>사용법</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>File-Setting-Live Templates-javascript</li>\n<li>abbreviation : prefix fc, Description : Function Componenets</li>\n<li>Template text : template 사용할 컴포넌트 작성</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token string\">'use strict'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n   * @param\r\n   * @constructor\r\n   */</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> $<span class=\"token constant\">FILE_NAME</span><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> $<span class=\"token constant\">FILE_NAME</span>$<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Edit validables 클릭 :\n<ul>\n<li>Template 등록($FILE_NAME$)</li>\n<li>Expression : fileNameWithoutExtension() 선택</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>vs code</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>사용법</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>snippet text : 사용할 javascript 컴포넌트 작성</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n\t<span class=\"token string\">\"use strict\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n\t * @param\r\n\t * @constructor\r\n\t */</span>\r\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token constant\">TM_FILENAME_BASE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token constant\">TM_FILENAME_BASE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://snippet-generator.app/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size=30px; color: #4dabf7; text-decoration:underline;\"><a href=\"https://snippet-generator.app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://snippet-generator.app</a></a> 홈페이지에서 vscode에 맞는 snippet 변환\n<ul>\n<li>Description : Function Componenets</li>\n<li>Tab trigger : fc</li>\n<li>your snippet : snippet text 붙이기</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>아래 변환된 snippet 텍스트 복사</li>\n<li>File-Preferences-User Snippets-javascript.json</li>\n<li>변환된 snippet 텍스트 붙이기</li>\n<li>js 파일 생성 후 fc tab할 시 등록한 snippet 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>","frontmatter":{"title":"web tools","date":"2020.04.12","category":"tools","tags":["Open Icon","Open Color","Surge","Snippet"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/base/2020-04-12-webtools/"}},
    "staticQueryHashes": ["4157816502"]}